snippet.title: TeleCollision Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
TeleCollision, demo coming soon! Trailer created by Daniel Jeppesen-Field.

Steam Listing - http://tinyurl.com/2z76scdb
Itch.io Listing - http://tinyurl.com/xrrxfy8
Website - https://telecollision.com/
Contact and Bug Reports - game@telecollision.com

TeleCollision is a pixelated RPG where fiction collides! After making your original character, you set out on a story of your choice. But something is off... And that gray man in the bowler keeps showing up...

Features
•Turn based combat with timing based attacks
•Character customization
•3 story paths to start with•Different builds to customize play style
•Collectible trading cards that grant different effects when equipped
•Large words probably used improperly
•A tiny cowboy who just wants to get ahead in life•Some jokes that might even be funny
•At least one vampire
